">0</span></span> <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.mk\">}</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Execution.html#Cslib.URM.Step.zero","kind":"ctor","line":61,"name":"Cslib.URM.Step.zero","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/Execution.lean#L61-L63"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Execution.html#Cslib.URM.Step\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">URM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Program\">Program</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State\">State</a> → <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State\">State</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Single-step execution relation for URMs.\n\nEach constructor corresponds to one of the four instruction types:\n- `zero`: Execute `Z n` (set register n to 0)\n- `succ`: Execute `S n` (increment register n)\n- `transfer`: Execute `T m n` (copy register m to register n)\n- `jump_eq`: Execute `J m n q` when registers m and n are equal (jump to q)\n- `jump_ne`: Execute `J m n q` when registers m and n differ (proceed to next)\n","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Execution.html#Cslib.URM.Step","kind":"inductive","line":50,"name":"Cslib.URM.Step","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/Execution.lean#L50-L77"}}],"imports":["Init","Cslib.Computability.URM.Basic","Cslib.Foundations.Data.Relation","Mathlib.Data.Part","Mathlib.Data.Setoid.Basic"],"instances":[{"className":"Setoid","name":"Cslib.URM.instSetoidProgram","typeNames":["Cslib.URM.Program"]}],"name":"Cslib.Computability.URM.Execution"}